{"tid":2350900,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美不滿中歐投資協定｜歐洲議會或以人權問題否決協定","createTime":"2021-01-02T17:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T17:45:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e79f068b53b96bcc3b825d9b966cbb8fb38863","tid":2350900,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯《紐約時報》稱，歐洲議會中有一大派反對這項協定，理由是它在阻止中國侵犯人權方面做得不夠。協定必須得到歐洲議會的批准才能生效。德國綠黨領袖、歐洲議會對華關係代表團主席Reinhard Butikofer表示，該協議應包括更強有力的保證，防止中國使用強迫勞動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/01/china-europe-agreement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fchina-europe-agreement%2F&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb0732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=2a6f8158\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/01/china-europe-agreement/</a>"},{"pid":"ab5eb4e10016541423069e2a1dd73f0a7a9d412b","tid":2350900,"uid":126317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"劇本一部分，歐洲佬最後咪又係乃共<br />\n<br />\n歐洲依家分分鐘仲淆仲等錢洗過共產黨<br />\n疫情下，經濟向北京求和<br />\n美國，五眼轉向亞太，國防向北京背後俄佬求和"},{"pid":"3126a84f077920aae1625efb808a2430438bb5f2","tid":2350900,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26248605d157ce68d360212ecb530acbff6c32c9","tid":2350900,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"人民幣真香"},{"pid":"761713537ab7f46d8f88ae780dfe7da56f1bce08","tid":2350900,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"由叫人唔好舉美國旗嘅講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘燈到歐洲議會全票通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}